 basis all students interested in option 2 long research paper will be graded on the honors pass system and will receive research credit number of units 3 course number 613 recently taught by janet martinez stephanie smith all dispute resolution mediation and negotiation courses alternate dispute resolution externship alternate dispute resolution law practice and policy dispute systems design international conflict resolution colloquium judgment and decision making mediation negotiation negotiation advanced international negotiation advanced transactions principles of contract design related links axess coursework digital reserve sls registrar related gould negotiation and mediation program rain 57 f 2012 stanford university system requirements help virtual tour
